name: Only Thieves Super Fan Lucky Boy # 1 Package Deal!
description: We think the name is pretty self-explanatory. Basically you get both CDs and either of the t-shirts... As well as a super secret prize to be determined by whatever is closest to us while we are packing it! Who knows? Maybe some cigarette butts, or a nudie magazine, a lock of hair (beard or otherwise). The possibilities are endless!

name: "Heartless Romantics" CD
description:
Our debut full-length. Ten tracks showcasing our binge drinking and sluttering abilities. Also there's so pretty cool songs on it. To be honest you can probably download it for free, but if you order it from us we'll send you some sweet stuff that you can't get from no torrent machine. 

TRACK LISTING
1. All the Sad Young Men
2. Discoveries
3. Flood Lights
4. Register
5. Pioneer Repair
6. The Ballad of the Aluminum Girl
7. Heartless Romantic
8. Unsatisfied 
9. Bricks
10. What's Wrong

name: Dire Wolf
description: There's not much we can say about this baby. It'll probably make you look like a bad ass. Printed on American Apparel so we gotta charge a little extra. It's also a v-neck so you can show off your chest piece/cleavage/man pelt/sweet gold medallions.

name: Rising Sun
description: Our tribute to the "Only Bad that Matters." Printed on super soft Tultex to give it that "brand-new-but-already-broken-in" feel! For any order over $1,000 we'll whisper the translation of the Japanese text into your ear.
